content:
I am saddened.
Haringey's in-house tree staff who I met were - in my experience - knowledgeable reliable & helpful. They could save a healthy tree from a chainsaw.
So why contract-out to people who don't seem, as Hamlet said: "to know a hawk from a handsaw."
